descriptionHtml:
[font=Courier New]A One time Limited beta file lol

[/font]There are some "Copyright" Names used here but hey! The Author im using on(J.R.R. Tolkein) Got some inspiration from other Tales so Im hoping its cool, besides nothing would please his creation then the spreading of its Religion lol jk or am I..?

It's my beta so Im aware of some spelling errors on orders, letters. I have a really weak pc so it takes a while to load the editor, im lazy to wait throught hte load screen at times, other times Im playing. x)
